text: I love mld. My next article may make that evident. It doesn’t belong everywhere but it has its place.

I'm not opposed to it, it's just hard to find playgroups that are cool with it.  And there really is nothing worse than someone blowing up the world out of desperation, just to grind the game out for another 2 hours.
That said, I'm *vehemently* opposed to this new idea out there that Boros' answer to ramp is MLD.  That's just not correct in my opinion, or even a strategy that has a chance or working.
[[Balancing Act]] is one thing.  Wiping out everyone's lands so the ramp deck can just ramp out again doesn't solve anything.
